 Timberlake. Typically, justified is pretty straight laced. It likes everything to be in it\'s place and not all cattywampus like the rest of the aligns. I am not saying that makes it better than the rest of the aligns, but it does tend to put off more of an elitist attitude.</p>','HTML Markup Test page','','inherit','closed','closed','','5-revision-v1','','','2022-05-03 14:51:01','2022-05-03 14:51:01','',5,'http://localhost/woodlandgroove/?p=82',0,'revision','',0),(83,1,'2022-05-03 14:51:33','2022-05-03 14:51:33','','Donate','','publish','closed','closed','','donate','','','2022-05-03 22:29:59','2022-05-03 22:29:59','',0,'http://localhost/woodlandgroove/?page_id=83',2,'page','',0),(84,1,'2022-05-03 14:51:33','2022-05-03 14:51:33','','Donate','','inherit','closed','closed','','83-revision-v1','','','2022-05-03 14:51:33','2022-05-03 14:51:33','',83,'http://localhost/woodlandgroove/?p=84',0,'revision','',0),(85,1,'2022-05-03 14:54:53','2022-05-03 14:54:53','','Home Page','','inherit','closed','closed','','15-revision-v1','','','2022-05-03 14:54:53','2022-05-03 14:54:53','',15,'http://localhost/woodlandgroove/?p=85',0,'revision','',0),(86,1,'2022-05-03 14:55:00','2022-05-03 14:55:00','','Home Page','','inherit','closed','closed','','15-revision-v1','','','2022-05-03 14:55:00','2022-05-03 14:55:00','',15,'http://localhost/woodlandgroove/?p=86',0,'revision','',0),(87,1,'2022-05-03 14:55:12','2022-05-03 14:55:12','','Home Page','','inherit','closed','closed','','15-revision-v1','','','2022-05-03 14:55:12','2022-05-03 14:55:12','',15,'http://localhost/woodlandgroove/?p=87',0,'revision','',0),(88,1,'2022-05-03 14:55:21','2022-05-03 14:55:21','','Home Page','','inherit','closed','closed','','15-revision-v1','','','2022-05-03 14:55:21','2022-05-03 14:55:21','',15,'http://localhost/woodlandgroove/?p=88',0,'revision','',0),(90,1,'2022-05-03 14:58:25','2022-05-03 14:58:25','a:8:{s:4:\"type\";s:3:\"tab\";s:12:\"instructions\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"required\";i:0;s:17:\"conditional_logic